		<label>Void Herald</label>
		<description>The Void Heralds are unique Coventech mechanoids which cannot fly long distances quickly, these wing's primary purpose is to constantly release a form of toxic gas Void Miasma, which blocks the sun and crystalizes nearly everything over time, some planets are entirely covered in this corrupting force, causing all those attempting to reach these planets to wither, die and crystalize.\n\n&lt;color=#FFA500&gt;Uses High Energy to fuel it's void beam, costs 5 for each charge cycle.&lt;/color&gt; \n\n&lt;color=#00ddc0&gt;Requires 30 bandwith, can house six advisory passengers, powered by mechanoid cells similar to those found in clusters.&lt;/color&gt; \n\n&lt;color=#FF0000&gt; Hostile Void Heralds will attempt to stay cause their Miasma to kill your colony, killing it quickly will be key, but if you can resist the toxic nature you could use it to harvest void crystals.&lt;/color&gt;</description>
		
